text: Jaroslav Svoboda (born 21 May 1944) is a Czech skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:People from Železný Brod Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1972 Winter Olympics
